            <h3>Purpose</h3>
            <p>
                The purpose of this website is to promote a white water rafting company by providing
                clear and engaging information about rafting trips, safety guidelines, pricing, and
                booking options. The site aims to attract adventure seekers, build trust with customers,
                and encourage visitors to plan and book a rafting experience.
            </p>
