        <section>
            <h3>Audience</h3>
            <p>
                The target audience includes outdoor enthusiasts, families, young adults, and groups
                between the ages of 18 and 55 who are interested in exciting and safe outdoor activities.
                Visitors will primarily access the site through mobile devices and laptops while planning
                vacations, weekend trips, or group adventures.
            </p>
